### Coming Soon
This page is going to explain how you can generate particle diagrams using the LaTeX tikz package or by using [Processing](https://processing.org/).

```
void mk_share(float x1, float y1, float x2, float y2, color c) {
  stroke(c);
  smooth();
  line(x1, y1, x2, y2);
}
```

